name: Mug'Zee, Heads of Security
description: Buddies from the day they were born, Mug'Zee's two heads are the topper of a giant hulk of an ogre enforcer, specifically hired by Gallywix to oversee his casino's day-to-day activities. In recent weeks, Mug'Zee's been reassigned to keep anyone and everyone out of the Gallagio's innermost chambers.

sections.title: Overview
sections.body_text:
The two heads of Mug'Zee, Mug and Zee, begin the encounter in a friendly contest to see who is in control. Whichever head has  players on their side of the arena becomes the Hspell:466376[Head Honcho], activating a unique set of abilities to unleash upon players.

Upon reaching 40% remaining health, Mug and Zee combine their efforts and attack in unison granting them the use of all of their abilities at once.

sections.title: Tanks
sections.body_text:
$bullet;Hspell:466518[Molten Gold Knuckles] inflict heavy damage in front of Mug and apply Hspell:467202[Golden Drip] to players hit.
$bullet;Damage from Hspell:469490[Double Whammy Shot] is mitigated by the closest player hit.

sections.title: Damage Dealers
sections.body_text:
$bullet;Hspell:472631[Earthshaker Gaols] splits damage among all players within the effect, trapping them within earthen walls.
$bullet;Touching Hspell:466539[Unstable Crawler Mines] causes them to explode, unleashing an Hspell:1220551[Unstable Cluster Bomb] and causing all players to suffer from Hspell:469043[Searing Shrapnel].

sections.title: Damage Dealers
sections.body_text:
$bullet;Hspell:472631[Earthshaker Gaols] splits damage among all players within the effect, trapping them within earthen walls.
$bullet;Hspell:466480[Frostshatter Spears] inflict lethal damage to the first player or Hspell:472631[Earthshaker Gaol] wall they hit.
$bullet;Touching Hspell:466539[Unstable Crawler Mines] causes them to explode, unleashing an Hspell:1220551[Unstable Cluster Bomb] and causing all players to suffer from Hspell:469043[Searing Shrapnel].

sections.title: Healers
sections.body_text:
$bullet;Hspell:468663[Elemental Calamity] and Hspell:469715[Uncontrolled Burn] inflict persistent damage over time each time Mug'zee swaps which head is the Hspell:466376[Head Honcho].
$bullet;Mug'Zee gains Hspell:466385[Moxie] the longer each head is in command.
